cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on using surround-view cameras to collect data for a 360-degree view of the area surrounding the vehicle. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper deals with self-driving cars and developing a driving model. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely category as the paper discusses learning a novel driving model. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper deals with developing an AI system for driving. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also a possible category as the paper discusses using a CAN bus reader to collect low-level driving maneuvers.
